data.title: Pushing Ice by Alastair Reynolds (English) Paperback Book
data.meta_description: Pushing Ice by Alastair Reynolds. Alastair Reynolds was born in Barry, South Wales. Author Alastair Reynolds. The icy mantle peels away to reveal that it was never a moon in the first place, just a parked spacecraft, millions of years old, that has now decided to move on.
data.text: Will ship within 5 business days of receiving cleared payment. The seller has specified an extended handling time for this item.
